So the agent has moved to the south, and is now at (40, 16), leaving the fountain at x=40 and y=15.

My strategy comes to mind: The boulder at (41, 15) is directly north of me. I can move east to (41, 16), then move north, pushing the boulder. I want to make sure I can do this and that my movement is legal.

